wasted like this!

00:22.160 --> 00:23.673
What the hell?

00:23.760 --> 00:25.910
What kind of Naples' team is this?

00:26.640 --> 00:29.871
How can you possibly play
such a crucial game this way?

00:29.960 --> 00:32.110
